hal \u0160kvarka]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=97|nat=HUN|name=[[Roland Varga (footballer)|Roland Varga]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=99|nat=HUN|name=[[D\u00e1vid Gr\u00f3f]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Players with multiple nationalities===\n* {{flagicon|HUN}} {{flagicon|NGA}} [[Kenneth Otigba]]\n* {{flagicon|HUN}} {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Leandro (Hungarian footballer)|Leandro]]\n* {{flagicon|GER}} {{flagicon|CRO}} [[Marcel Heister]]\n* {{flagicon|NOR}} {{flagicon|SSD}} [[Tokmac Nguen]]\n\n====Out on loan====\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=23|nat=HUN|name=[[Luk\u00e1cs B\u0151le]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Zalaegerszegi TE|Zalaegerszegi]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=42|nat=HUN|name=[[\u00c1d\u00e1m Varga (footballer)|\u00c1d\u00e1m Varga]]|pos=GK|other=at [[Soroks\u00e1r SC|Soroks\u00e1r]]}}\n{{Fs player|no= 3|nat=HUN|name=Zsombor Tak\u00e1cs|pos=DF|other=at [[Soroks\u00e1r SC|Soroks\u00e1r]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=  |nat=HUN|name=[[Erik Silye]]|pos=DF|other=at [[Mez\u0151k\u00f6vesdi SE|Mez\u0151k\u00f6vesd]]}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=  |nat=HUN|name=[[Korn\u00e9l Csernik]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Soroks\u00e1r SC|Soroks\u00e1r]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=  |nat=SRB|name=[[Dejan Georgijevi\u0107]]|pos=FW|other=at [[FC Irtysh Pavlodar|Irtysh Pavlodar]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=  |nat=ITA|name=[[Davide Lanzafame]]|pos=FW|other=at [[Budapest Honv\u00e9d FC|Honv\u00e9d]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Retired numbers===\n[[File:Simon Tibor \u00dcll\u0151i \u00fat 129..jpg|thumb|right|250px|[[Tibor Simon]]'s memorial]]\n* <big>'''2'''</big>&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|HUN}} [[Tibor Simon]], [[defender (football)|Defender]] (1985\u201399)&nbsp;\u2013 ''posthumous honour.''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/news/newsid=22246.html|title=Sopron coach dies after attack|date=24 April 2002|publisher=UEFA}}</ref>\n* <big>'''12'''</big>&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|HUN}} \"[[12th man (football)|The 12th man]]\", reserved for club supporters. Number retired in 2007.\n\n===Notable former players===\nHad senior international cap(s