]]\n|1967-69\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[G\u00e9za Kalocsay]]\n|1970\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Jen\u0151 Dalnoki]]\n|1970\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Ferenc Csan\u00e1di]]\n|1970-73\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Dezs\u0151 Nov\u00e1k]]\n|1973\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Jen\u0151 Dalnoki]]\n|1973-78\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Zolt\u00e1n Friedmanszky]]\n|1978-80\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Dezs\u0151 Nov\u00e1k]]\n|1980-83\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[G\u00e9za Vincze]]\n|1984-85\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 S\u00e1rosi]]\n|1985\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Jen\u0151 Dalnoki]]\n|1985-87\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Gyula R\u00e1kosi]]\n|1987-90\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Tibor Nyilasi]]\n|1990-94\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Dezs\u0151 Nov\u00e1k]]\n|1994-96\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[J\u00f3zsef Mucha]]\n|1996\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Zolt\u00e1n Varga (footballer, born 1945)|Zolt\u00e1n Varga]]\n|1996-97\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Tibor Nyilasi]]\n|1997-98\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Croatia}} [[Marijan Vlak]]\n|1999\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[J\u00f3zsef Mucha]]\n|1999\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Croatia}} [[Stanko Poklepovi\u0107]]\n|1999-2000\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[J\u00e1nos Csank]]\n|2000-01\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[J\u00f3zsef Garami]]\n|2002-03\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Attila Pint\u00e9r]]\n|2004\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Csaba L\u00e1szl\u00f3]]\n|2004-05\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Imre Gellei]]\n|2005-07\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Serbia}} [[Zoran Kunti\u0107]]\n|2007\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[J\u00e1nos Csank]]\n|2007-08\n|-\n|{{flagicon|England}} [[Bobby Davidson]]\n|2008-09\n|-\n|{{flagicon|England}} [[Craig Short]]\n|2009-10\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 Prukner]]\n|2010-11\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Tam\u00e1s Nagy]]\n|2011\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Lajos D\u00e9t\u00e1ri]]\n|2011-12\n|-\n|{{flagicon|The Netherlands}} [[Ricardo Moniz]]\n|2012-13\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Germany}} [[Thomas Doll]]\n|2013-2018\n|-