67\u201368 Inter-Cities Fairs Cup|1967\u201368]]\n*'''[[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup]]'''\n**Runners-up (1): [[1974\u201375 European Cup Winners' Cup|1974\u201375]]\n*'''[[Mitropa Cup]]'''\n** '''Winners (2)''': [[1928 Mitropa Cup|1928]], [[1937 Mitropa Cup|1937]]\n**Runners-up (4): [[1935 Mitropa Cup|1935]], [[1938 Mitropa Cup|1938]], [[1939 Mitropa Cup|1939]], [[1940 Mitropa Cup|1940]]\n*'''[[Challenge Cup (Austro-Hungarian Empire)|Challenge Cup]]'''\n**'''Winners (1)''': 1909\n**Runners-up (1): 1911\n*'''[[Tournoi de N\u00f6el de Paris]]'''\n**'''Winners (1)''': 1935<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesp/paris-tourn.html|title=International Tournaments (Paris) 1904-1935|author=|date=|website=www.rsssf.com}}</ref>\n\n;Notes\n*<span id=\"notes_qr12\"></span>Note 12: more than any other Hungarian football club.\n*<span id=\"notes_qr13\"></span>Note 13: more than any other Hungarian football club.\n\n==Players==\n===First team squad===\n{{Updated|11 January 2020.}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fradi.hu/labdarugas/elso-csapat/jatekoskeret|title=Ferencvaros - First team squad|website=www.fradi.hu|language=hu|access-date=2019-08-01}}</ref>\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no= 1|nat=HUN|name=[[Gerg\u0151 Sz\u00e9csi]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no= 5|nat=GHA|name=[[Abraham Frimpong]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no= 7|nat=BRA|name=[[Wergiton do Rosario Calmon|Som\u00e1lia]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no= 8|nat=HUN|name=[[Gerg\u0151 Lovrencsics]]|pos=DF|other=[[Captain (association football)|vice-captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=10|nat=NOR|name=[[Tokmac Nguen]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=11|nat=UKR|name=[[Oleksandr Zubkov]]|pos=MF|other=<small>on loan from [[FC Shakhtar Donetsk|Shakhtar]]</small>}}\n{{Fs player|no=14|nat=UKR|name=[[Ihor Kharatin]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=16|nat=HUN|name=[[Leandro (Hungarian footballer)|Leandro]]|pos=DF|other=[[Captain (association football)|captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=17|nat=BIH|name=[[Eldar \u0106ivi\u0107]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=18|nat=HUN|name=[[D\u00e1vid Sig\u00e9r]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=19|nat=HUN|name=[[B\u00e1lint V\u00e9csei]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=20|nat=BLR|name=[[Mikalay Signevich]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=21|nat=HUN|name=[[Endre Botka]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=HUN|name=[[Kenneth Otigba]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=25|nat=SVN|name=[[Miha Bla\u017ei\u010d (footballer)|Miha Bla\u017ei\u010d]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=26|nat=GER|name=[[Marcel Heister]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=27|nat=ARG|name=[[Gast\u00f3n Lodico]]|pos=MF|other=<small>on loan from [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Lan\u00fas|Lan\u00fas]]</small>}}\n{{Fs player|no=33|nat=GEO|name=[[Lasha Dvali]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=51|nat=HUN|name=[[Andr\u00e1s Csonka]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=53|nat=HUN|name=Dominik Csontos|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=69|nat=HUN|name=Reg\u0151 Sz\u00e1nth\u00f3|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=70|nat=CIV|name=[[Franck Boli]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=77|nat=HUN|name=[[Krisztofer Szeret\u0151]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=88|nat=BRA|name=[[Isael da Silva Barbosa|Isael]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=90|nat=HUN|name=[[D\u00e9nes Dibusz]]|pos=GK|other=[[Captain (association football)|3rd captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=92|nat=SVK|name=[[Michal \u0160kvarka]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=97|nat=HUN|name=[[Roland Varga (footballer)|Roland Varga]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=99|nat=HUN|name=[[D\u00e1vid Gr\u00f3f]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Players with multiple nationalities===\n* {{flagicon|HUN}} {{flagicon|NGA}} [[Kenneth Otigba]]\n* {{flagicon|HUN}} {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Leandro (Hungarian footballer)|Leandro]]\n* {{flagicon|GER}} {{flagicon|CRO}} [[Marcel Heister]]\n* {{flagicon|NOR}} {{flagicon|SSD}} [[Tokmac Nguen]]\n\n====Out on loan====\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=23|nat=HUN|name=[[Luk\u00e1cs B\u0151le]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Zalaegerszegi TE|Zalaegerszegi]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=42|nat=HUN|name=[[\u00c1d\u00e1m Varga (footballer)|\u00c1d\u00e1m Varga]]|pos=GK|other=at [[Soroks\u00e1r SC|Soroks\u00e1r]]}}\n{{Fs player|no= 3|nat=HUN|name=Zsombor Tak\u00e1cs|pos=DF|other=at [[Soroks\u00e1r SC|Soroks\u00e1r]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=  |nat=HUN|name=[[Erik Silye]]|pos=DF|other=at [[Mez\u0151k\u00f6vesdi SE|Mez\u0151k\u00f6vesd]]}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=  |nat=HUN|name=[[Korn\u00e9l Csernik]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Soroks\u00e1r SC|Soroks\u00e1r]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=  |nat=SRB|name=[[Dejan Georgijevi\u0107]]|pos=FW|other=at [[FC Irtysh Pavlodar|Irtysh Pavlodar]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=  |nat=ITA|name=[[Davide Lanzafame]]|pos=FW|other=at [[Budapest Honv\u00e9d FC|Honv\u00e9d]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Retired numbers===\n[[File:Simon Tibor \u00dcll\u0151i \u00fat 129..jpg|thumb|right|250px|[[Tibor Simon]]'s memorial]]\n* <big>'''2'''</big>&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|HUN}} [[Tibor Simon]], [[defender (football)|Defender]] (1985\u201399)&nbsp;\u2013 ''posthumous honour.''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/news/newsid=22246.html|title=Sopron coach dies after attack|date=24 April 2002|publisher=UEFA}}</ref>\n* <big>'''12'''</big>&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|HUN}} \"[[12th man (football)|The 12th man]]\", reserved for club supporters. Number retired in 2007.\n\n===Notable former players===\nHad senior international cap(s) for their respective countries.\nPlayers whose name is listed in '''bold''' represented their countries while playing for Ferencv\u00e1ros.\n{{For|a list of all former and current Ferencv\u00e1rosi TC players with a Wikipedia article|Category:Ferencv\u00e1rosi TC footballers }}\n{{col-begin-small}}\n{{col-4}}\n*{{flagicon|TTO}} [[Akeem Adams]] [[#notes qr11|<sup>11</sup>]]\n*{{flagicon|HUN}} '''[[Fl\u00f3ri\u00e1n Albert]]''' [[#notes qr4|<sup>4</sup>]] [[#notes qr5|<sup>5</sup>]]\n*{{flagicon|HUN}} '''[[Fl\u00f3ri\u00e1n Albert, Jr.]]'''\n*{{flagicon|MKD}} [[Aleksandar Bajevski]]\n*{{flagicon|HUN}} '''[[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 B\u00e1lint]]''' [[#notes qr6|<sup>6</sup>]]\n*{{flagicon|HUN}} '''[[Zolt\u00e1n Balogh (footballer)|Zolt\u00e1n Balogh]]'''\n*{{flagicon|HUN}} '''[[Zsolt B\u00e1r\u00e1nyos]]'''\n