y}} [[Lajos Dim\u00e9ny]]\n|1939-42\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Istv\u00e1n T\u00f3th (footballer)|Istv\u00e1n T\u00f3th-Potya]]\n|1943\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Alfr\u00e9d Schaffer]]\n|1943-44\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Elem\u00e9r Berkessy]]\n|1944\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[P\u00e1l Szab\u00f3]]\n|1945\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[G\u00e1bor Urbancsik]]\n|1945-46\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Lajos Dim\u00e9ny]]\n|1946-47\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Zolt\u00e1n Opata]]\n|1947\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Antal Lyka]]\n|1948-1950\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Mikl\u00f3s Vadas]]\n|1950\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[G\u00e1bor Urbancsik]]\n|1951\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Ferenc De\u00e1k (footballer)|Ferenc De\u00e1k]]\n|1952-53\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[K\u00e1roly S\u00f3s]]\n|1953-56\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[\u00c1rp\u00e1d Csan\u00e1di]]\n|1957\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[S\u00e1ndor T\u00e1trai]]\n|1958-61\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[J\u00f3zsef M\u00e9sz\u00e1ros]]\n|1961-1965\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Oszk\u00e1r Vizse\u00e1l]]\n|1965\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[S\u00e1ndor T\u00e1trai]]\n|1966\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[K\u00e1roly Lakat]]\n|1967-69\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[G\u00e9za Kalocsay]]\n|1970\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Jen\u0151 Dalnoki]]\n|1970\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Ferenc Csan\u00e1di]]\n|1970-73\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Dezs\u0151 Nov\u00e1k]]\n|1973\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Jen\u0151 Dalnoki]]\n|1973-78\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Zolt\u00e1n Friedmanszky]]\n|1978-80\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Dezs\u0151 Nov\u00e1k]]\n|1980-83\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[G\u00e9za Vincze]]\n|1984-85\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 S\u00e1rosi]]\n|1985\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Jen\u0151 Dalnoki]]\n|1985-87\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Gyula R\u00e1kosi]]\n|1987-90\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Tibor Nyilasi]]\n|1990-94\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Dezs\u0151 Nov\u00e1k]]\n|1994-96\n|-\n|{{flagico