ik]] || {{age|1985|06|01}} || Right-handed || rowspan = \"2\"  {{n/a}} || [[Tamil Nadu cricket team|Tamil Nadu]] || [[South Zone cricket team|South]] || {{n/a}} || ODI, T20I || 21\n|-\n| [[Rishabh Pant]] || {{age|1997|10|04}} || Left-handed \n || [[Delhi cricket team|Delhi]] || [[North Zone cricket team|North]] \n| align=center| A || Test, ODI, T20I || 17\n|-\n| [[Sanju Samson]] || {{age|1994|11|11}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|medium]] || [[Kerala cricket team|Kerala]] || [[South Zone cricket team|South]] || {{n/a}} || T20I || 9\n|-\n| [[Wriddhiman Saha]] || {{age|1984|10|24}} || Right-handed || {{n/a}} || [[Bengal cricket team|Bengal]] || [[East Zone cricket team|East]] || align=center| B || Test || 6\n|-\n! colspan=\"10\" | Pace bowlers\n|-\n| [[Khaleel Ahmed]] || {{age|1997|12|05}} || Right-handed || Left-arm [[Fast bowling|medium-fast]] || [[Rajasthan cricket team|Rajasthan]] || [[Central Zone cricket team|Central]] || {{n/a}} || ODI, T20I || 27\n|-\n| [[Jasprit Bumrah]] || {{age|1993|12|06}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|fast-medium]] || [[Gujarat cricket team|Gujarat]] || [[West Zone cricket team|West]] || align=center| A+ || Test, ODI, T20I || 93 \n|-\n| [[Deepak Chahar]] || {{age|1992|08|07}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|medium-fast]] || [[Rajasthan cricket team|Rajasthan]] || [[Central Zone cricket team|Central]] || align=center| C || ODI, T20I || 90\n|-\n| [[Siddarth Kaul]] || {{age|1990|05|19}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|medium-fast]] || [[Punjab cricket team (India)|Punjab]] || [[North Zone cricket team|North]] || {{n/a}} || T20I || 36\n|-\n| [[Bhuvneshwar Kumar]] || {{age|1990|02|05}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|medium-fast]] || [[Uttar Pradesh cricket team|Uttar Pradesh]] || [[Central Zone cricket team|Central]] || align=center| A || ODI, T20I || 15\n|-\n| [[Shardul Thakur]] || {{age|1991|10|16}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|medium-fast]] || [[Mumbai cricket t